* All of a sudden?!?

No, VW has specified the correct tire to be either a reinforced sidewall or a Commercial tire since the mid
70's in print. Go read page 53 of the 79 owners manual
http://bama.ua.edu/~darren/vw/Page53.html

On the Tire Sticky on the Samba website, I posted pics of page 51 of the 78 owners manual but the website is
gone now.
